@group tracking
@endpoint DELETE /tracking/v0/trackers/{TrackerName}
@desc Deletes a tracker resource from your Amazon Web Services account.  This operation deletes the resource permanently. If the tracker resource is in use, you may encounter an error. Make sure that the target resource isn't a dependency for your applications.
@required {TrackerName: str}

@endgroup

